{"tid":2344964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「12港人案」被批「秘密審訊」 中駐英大使館：中国是法治国家","createTime":"2020-12-29T07:09:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T07:15:04.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"46f12d2eda792ae62b51d3fb15085199e35049a9","tid":2344964,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T07:09:39.000Z","msg":"欲在8月間偷渡台灣失敗後，遭押往中國廣東省的12名香港青年，其中10人的案件已於昨日下午在深圳鹽田法院完成聆訊並「認罪」，但庭審期間，法院頻頻找藉口拒絕家屬、委派律師、記者及各國外交人員旁聽，讓英國外相藍韜文（Dominic Raab）批12人根本是被「秘密審訊」。對此，中國駐英大使館立刻回嗆，「中國是法治國家」、「英方相關言論混淆是非中方堅決反對」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3395337\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3395337&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9UzxzvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=ad4939e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3395337&h=c146663c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3395337</a>"},{"pid":"95f48e434e56ea0775a22d65c982177a313a7ac2","tid":2344964,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T07:15:04.000Z","msg":"中原自三皇五帝起已經有法治，朕即法律 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}